{
  "stem": "21089.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He-- they, they requested all the glass, all the private glass.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was putting the glass specially in the-- where they used to live when his family used to come.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said, you know, I need a helper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe you will help me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about the glass, and this I was-- [INAUDIBLE] helping him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we've been-- any transportation we used-- we received, a half-track of ration, army [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they help loaded the glass, and we've been coming to a different place-- private places, offices.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he has-- he, he was surprised how much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He made more money over this than he made making in long time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was helping him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was also mirrors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was cutting mirrors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was a big deal for Russian families, a big piece of mirror.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you wouldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I s-- I didn't believe myself when the first time I encountered the Russian soldiers, you know, the rifles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Some of them had a string.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some of them had been tied up with the knots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Their clothes was like a rags.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "No uniforms, but rag uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was surprised because I always think is that Russian army is as strong, strong army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this was in 1939 were the first time the world saw the Russian army, and the army saw, saw what is going in the west.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The same thing was they saw a watch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They would give anything so he would sell him their watch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Don't have to be good watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Don't have to be a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "As long as he had the watch on his hand, he was very proud.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "When he was to-- and this is the truth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This no joke.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
